title: Coronavirus: First US death was three weeks earlier than initially believed, showing how behind the country was in battling pandemic
description: California health officials discover Santa Clara County death was nearly a month before Seattle-area patient died from Covid-19, believed to be first in country
content:
The first coronavirus death in the US happened several weeks earlier than initial reports believed, according to autopsies performed in California, underlining how far behind the country was in stopping the spread.
